name: Windmill and Wyse
description:
This week we will make our way down Wyse Rd to the smoke stacks and then back via Windmill, Alderney, and Ochterloney.
Now that it is getting dark out early, don't forget to wear some brightly coloured clothes or light up gear.
As always, we meet at the Sullivans Pond Gazebo at 6:30pm.
